					Eagle PRODUCTION
					Business Card Designer PRO 7.1 + KeyMaker
Business card creator 	
    * Buy business card designer
	* System Requirements:
	* Windows 98/ME/2000/2003/NT/XP/Vista
	* 64 MB of RAM and less than 30 MB of hard drive space.
   
More features...
	* Save as template: You can create your own custom templates easily, and reuse it later. 
	* Cut-Copy-Paste: Offers cut-copy-paste functionality for all the design elements. 
		You can also copy-paste texts and images from other applications.
	* Undo/Redo: Supports Undo/Redo.
	* Align/Rotate: You can align the selected elements to the right, left, top or bottom, 
		or can rotate them to any desired angle. 
		
Use this business card software to design and print spectacular business cards in a matter 
of minutes - on your own printer, on card stocks from Avery, Sigel, Herma, Formtec, DECAdry etc. 
This is a professional quality Business Card Maker and printing software.
You can create cards with text, shapes, logos, color blends and more. Use supplied templates and 
backgrounds to create professional cards quickly.
Create one or two-sided cards, horizontal or vertical cards. Add shadow to text, rotate text or 
art-work and more. You can find a lot of pre-designed "Business Card Templates" for all business 
types that can be used to easily design your card.
